cation and robust design and system level challenges for nextgen last modified tue 7 feb 2012 at 18 48 publications title author s journal date 2010 2 18 find a faculty member stay connected itunes icon google+ icon facebook icon twitter icon linkedin icon stanford university school of engineering 475 via ortega stanford california 94305 4121 650.725 1575 1997 2012 stanford university all rights reserved accreditation info terms of use copyright complaints contact us
